"""
    utility function to make a file unique as never used before
    """
a = random.randint(1, 10000000)
a = random.randint(a, a + 400)
a = '// ' + str(a) + ' unique_id'
shutil.copy(loc + '/one.cpp', loc + '/hidden_one.cpp')
with open(loc + '/hidden_one.cpp', 'r+') as f:
    content = f.read()
    f.seek(0, 0)
    f.write(content + a + '\n')
